ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with BBC Golf Ltd. ** NCC **
PrecisOrder Approving that the National Capital Commission grant an option to extend the lease with BBC GOLF Ltd., operating as Club de Golf Champlain, and Stan Brigham, as the indemnifier, for a period of ten years, beginning on April 1, 2020, for the real property located at 1145 chemin d'Aylmer, in Gatineau, Quebec.
